      <section xml:id="vdbenginefirebdinst">
        <title>Install and configure the Firebird ODBC Driver</title>
        <para>The Virtuoso Virtual Database engine uses ODBC as the connectivity mechanism for linking
remote database objects into its local schema. Thus a Firebird ODBC Driver must be available with a
suitably configured DSN for connecting to the target database.</para>
